  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the National Action Plan for Ready-made Garment Sector in Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve working conditions in the garment sector in Bangladesh by providing support to structural and fire assessments on around 1500 factories, strengthening the labour and factory inspection regime, providing occupational health and safety training to garment sector employees and increasing national health and safety awareness through media campaigns,  improving dialogue between workers and management at individual factory and national level and supporting the rehabilitation of the survivors of recent industrial accidents.</narrative>
  </description>
